</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="74.[684,1213,291,1736]" pageId="74" pageNumber="74">
VOUCHER MATERIAL (TOTAL = 2): Nuevo 
<collectingRegion country="Trinidad and Tobago" name="San Juan/Laventille" pageId="74" pageNumber="74">San Juan</collectingRegion>
(AMNH 273075; MUSM 15212); see table 33 for measurements.
</paragraph>
